373
00:23:54,380 --> 00:23:57,210
派一支搜查队搜查天空和地面
Let's get a search team on the ground, scouts in the air.

374
00:23:57,210 --> 00:23:59,250
没牙仔和我去沿海岸线巡逻
Toothless and I will fly the coastline.

375
00:23:59,250 --> 00:24:03,220
我不建议你带没牙仔出去  首领
Yeah, I wouldn't advise taking Toothless anywhere, Chief.

376
00:24:03,220 --> 00:24:05,390
