I know this handiwork.

377
00:24:05,390 --> 00:24:08,720
恐惧格里莫  在我那儿可是个有名的家伙
Grimmel the Grisly. Famous back where I'm from.

378
00:24:08,720 --> 00:24:11,030
我见过的最聪明的捕龙猎手
The smartest dragon hunter I ever met.

379
00:24:11,030 --> 00:24:13,130
当然了  不及我
Well, next to me, of course.

380
00:24:13,130 --> 00:24:16,330
