Well, he can't be that smart. He left his trap unmanned.

381
00:24:16,330 --> 00:24:20,670
老格里莫做的任何事都不是随意的
Nothing's accidental when it comes to old Grimmel.

382
00:24:20,670 --> 00:24:22,340
