He lives for the hunt,

383
00:24:22,340 --> 00:24:24,340
懂他猎物的一举一动
to get inside the mind of his prey,

384
00:24:24,340 --> 00:24:26,810
把它们所有的选择都掌控在手中
to control its every choice.

385
00:24:26,810 --> 00:24:28,370
对他来说  一切都是一场游戏
It's all a game to him.

386
00:24:28,380 --> 00:24:30,310
他不知道他遇上的对手是谁
Well, he doesn't know who he's playing with.

387
00:24:30,310 --> 00:24:32,310
