Yeah. Well, we've dealt with his kind before.

388
00:24:32,310 --> 00:24:34,350
别小瞧了他  小嗝嗝
Don't underestimate him, Hiccup.

389
00:24:34,350 --> 00:24:37,080
记住我说的话  他会回来的
Mark my words. He'll be back.

390
00:24:37,090 --> 00:24:39,690
我们就等他来
Then we'll be waiting for him.

391
00:24:53,690 --> 00:24:54,430
好了
All right.

392
00:24:54,440 --> 00:24:56,840
好吧  给我点线索
All right, come on, give me a clue here.

393
