May I?

401
00:25:49,760 --> 00:25:50,890
小嗝嗝首领
Chief Hiccup.

402
00:25:50,890 --> 00:25:54,930
我该叫你首领还是小嗝嗝
Hmm? Do I say Chief or do I call you Hiccup?

403
00:25:54,930 --> 00:25:56,200
你喜欢哪个
What do you prefer?

404
00:25:58,450 --> 00:26:02,900
你根本不知道我是谁  对吗
You have no idea who I am, do you?

405
00:26:04,770 --> 00:26:07,010
你父亲认识我
Well, your father knew of me.

406
00:26:07,010 --> 00:26:09,910
曾经有一个首领
Now, there was a chief.

407
00:26:09,910 --> 00:26:14,520
他是最厉害的捕龙猎手
One of the greatest dragon hunters to have ever lived.

408
00:26:14,520 --> 00:26:17,080
他会怎么想你
What would he think of you?

409
00:26:20,520 --> 00:26:22,220
他做得没错
He had it right, you know.

410
00:26:22,220 --> 00:26:24,220
为了让你能在一个更好的世界中成长
Making it his mission to destroy the beasts

411
00:26:24,230 --> 00:26:26,490
而将消灭那些怪兽作为己任
so that you could grow up in a better world.

412
00:26:26,490 --> 00:26:28,460
