He changed his mind.

413
00:26:28,460 --> 00:26:30,830
看看他落得什么下场
And look where that got him.

414
00:26:32,330 --> 00:26:35,540
我们还是直奔主题吧
So let's get to the point.

415
00:26:35,540 --> 00:26:38,240
我是夜煞杀手
I am the Night Fury killer.

416
00:26:38,240 --> 00:26:42,810
我杀死了每一只夜煞  除了你的
I've hunted every last one but yours.

417
00:26:42,810 --> 00:26:45,410
你要把那条龙交给我  不然我...
You are going to give me that dragon, or I will...

418
00:26:45,410 --> 00:26:47,310
我永远不会交出他
I will never give him up.

419
00:26:49,480 --> 00:26:54,320
你希望龙和我们平等自由地相处吗
You wish dragons to live free among us like equals?

420
00:26:56,190 --> 00:26:58,390
这种观念有毒  孩子
A toxic notion, my boy.

421
00:26:58,390 --> 00:27:02,030
历史证明我们是更高级的种族
History has shown that we are the superior species.

422
00:27:02,030 --> 00:27:06,500
万一你的错误观念流传开来怎么办
What if word of your misguided ideas were to spread?

423
00:27:06,500 --> 00:27:09,600
据我们所知  那样简直就是
