You think you can come into my home,

429
00:27:30,930 --> 00:27:35,090
坐在我父亲的椅子上  威胁我的龙吗
sit in my father's chair, and threaten my dragon?

430
00:27:35,660 --> 00:27:37,060
这里是伯克岛
This is Berk.

431
00:27:37,070 --> 00:27:40,570
我们从比你恶劣百万倍的人手中守护了自己的家园
And we have defended our way of life from far worse than you.

432
00:27:42,340 --> 00:27:45,270
有战斗精神  我喜欢
A fighting spirit. I love it.

433
00:27:45,270 --> 00:27:48,610
恐怕你搞错了
Only I'm afraid you're mistaken.

434
00:27:48,610 --> 00:27:52,250
你从来没有见过像我这样的人
You've never seen anything like me.

435
00:28:01,320 --> 00:28:02,530
阿斯翠德  小心
Astrid, look out!

436
00:28:09,630 --> 00:28:11,630
-小心  -孩子  快跑
- Look out! - Son, get clear.

437
00:28:13,970 --> 00:28:15,900
快跑
Run!

438
00:28:23,240 --> 00:28:25,550
在我下次来之前
Have my dragon ready

439
00:28:25,550 --> 00:28:30,550
准备好我要的龙  不然我会毁掉你爱的一切
when I return, or I will destroy everything you love.

440
00:28:43,930 --> 00:28:45,930
-进去  -大半夜的
- Inside. - It's the middle of the night.

441
00:28:45,930 --> 00:28:48,200
-我们来这里干什么  -好了
- What are we doing here? - All right.

442
00:28:48,200 --> 00:28:50,970
好了  大家安静一下
All right, everybody. Settle down, please.

443
00:28:52,110 --> 00:28:54,010
鱼脚司
Fishlegs.

444
00:28:54,010 --> 00:28:56,440
你见过那种龙吗
Have you ever seen that species of dragon before?

445
00:28:59,320 --> 00:29:00,380
让我去和他战斗
Let me at him!

446
00:29:00,380 --> 00:29:02,210
我要让他尝尝我的厉害
I'll give him a piece of my mind!

447
00:29:02,220 --> 00:29:05,020
厉害就是指我的拳头
And by mind, I mean fist!

448
00:29:05,020 --> 00:29:07,520
你们忘了大家差点丧命吗
Did you miss the part where we almost died?

449
00:29:07,880 --> 00:29:10,160
你们没看到我的房子吗
Have you seen my house?

450
00:29:10,160 --> 00:29:12,630
这是新的敌人
This is a new kind of enemy.

451
00:29:12,630 --> 00:29:15,300
我低估了他  这是我的错
And I underestimated him. Now, that's on me.

452
00:29:15,650 --> 00:29:17,300
但我不会再犯这样的错误了
But I will not do that again.

453
00:29:17,960 --> 00:29:20,530
我们是维京人  我们不会临阵逃脱
We're Vikings. We don't run from a fight.

454
00:29:20,540 --> 00:29:23,220
至少我不会  你可能会
At least, I don't. You might.

455
00:29:23,220 --> 00:29:24,500
我同意小嗝嗝
I agree with Hiccup.

456
00:29:24,510 --> 00:29:26,510
我们还没见识过格里莫真正的手段
We haven't seen the last of Grimmel.

457
00:29:26,510 --> 00:29:29,410
他是一个耐心  专注的捕猎者
He's a predator, single-minded and patient.

458
00:29:29,410 --> 00:29:31,580
他得不到他想要的东西是不会停手的
He won't stop until he gets what he wants.

459
00:29:31,580 --> 00:29:32,680
我支持艾瑞特
I'm with Eret.

460
00:29:32,680 --> 00:29:35,680
我们必须认真对待这次威胁
We have to take this threat seriously.

461
00:29:35,680 --> 00:29:37,680
格里莫只是一个征兆
Grimmel is just a sign of the times.

462
00:29:37,690 --> 00:29:41,120
我们的敌人愈发聪明  执拗
Our enemies are getting smarter, more determined.

463
00:29:41,120 --> 00:29:45,560
我们不仅人数占劣势  还将弱点暴露在明处
We're not just overcrowded. We are exposed and vulnerable.

464
00:29:45,560 --> 00:29:49,160
无法应付全面战争  要拿我们爱的人涉险
Short of full-blown war and risking everyone we love,

465
00:29:49,160 --> 00:29:52,430
我觉得...
I don't...

466
00:29:52,430 --> 00:29:55,770
我觉得我们不该再留在这里了
I don't see a way of staying here any longer.

467
00:29:55,770 --> 00:29:57,540
斯多戈会怎么想
What would Stoick think of this?

468
00:29:57,540 --> 00:30:00,110
听他说完
Hey! Hear him out!

469
00:30:06,180 --> 00:30:09,520
如果我们想和我们的龙和平共处
If we want to live in peace with our dragons,

470
00:30:09,520 --> 00:30:11,550
我们需要一个更好的计划
we need a better plan.

471
00:30:11,550 --> 00:30:14,250
你有什么想法  首领
So what are you saying, Chief?

472
00:30:14,260 --> 00:30:16,420
我想说  我们要消失
I'm saying we have to disappear.

473
00:30:16,420 --> 00:30:18,360
消失在地图上
Off the map.

474
00:30:18,360 --> 00:30:21,590
带这些龙去一个没人能找到他们的地方
Take the dragons to a place where no one will find them.

475
00:30:21,600 --> 00:30:23,600
那是哪里
And where might that be?

476
00:30:23,600 --> 00:30:26,430
他是说要去寻找秘密世界
He's talking about a quest for the Hidden World.

477
00:30:26,430 --> 00:30:27,300
秘密什么
The hidden what?

478
00:30:27,300 --> 00:30:29,440
-白日做梦  -没错
- Out to lunch. - Yeah.

479
00:30:29,440 --> 00:30:32,440
我小时候  我父亲就一心想找到那里
My father was obsessed with it when I was a boy.

480
00:30:32,440 --> 00:30:34,210
他绘制了地图  记录了笔记
He made notes and maps

481
00:30:34,210 --> 00:30:38,050
寻找深藏在世界边缘
in search of the ancestral home of all dragons,

482
00:30:38,050 --> 00:30:41,280
所有龙的故土
tucked away somewhere beyond the edge of the world.

483
00:30:41,280 --> 00:30:43,420
这也许是我们想要的解决办法
It may be the solution we need.

484
00:30:44,030 --> 00:30:46,250
我们是龙的子民
We are dragon people.

485
00:30:46,250 --> 00:30:48,350
我们属于那里
It's where we belong.

486
00:30:48,360 --> 00:30:52,360
我知道这里是我们的家
Look, I know this is our home.

487
00:30:52,360 --> 00:30:55,130
我的父亲把这里交给我来守护
My father left me to protect it.

488
00:30:55,130 --> 00:30:58,130
但是伯克岛不仅仅只是这个地方
But Berk is more than this place.

489
00:30:58,130 --> 00:31:00,070
我们才是伯克
We are Berk.

490
00:31:00,070 --> 00:31:01,700
这些人民  这些龙
The people, the dragons.

491
00:31:01,700 --> 00:31:05,470
我们去哪里  伯克就在哪里
I say Berk is wherever we go.

492
00:31:08,180 --> 00:31:11,180
我支持他  还有谁
I'm with him! Who else?!

493
00:31:30,260 --> 00:31:31,660
不好意思  让一下
Excuse me. Coming through.

494
00:31:31,670 --> 00:31:33,770
让我过去一下
Just, let me just get right through here.

495
00:31:33,770 --> 00:31:37,600
鱼肉仔  来吃石头  吃石头
Fishmeat, look, eat your rocks. Eat your rocks.

496
00:31:37,610 --> 00:31:40,110
天  带宝宝飞的人实在是太没素质了
Gods! People who fly with babies are the worst.

497
00:31:42,280 --> 00:31:44,840
我觉得我总是在问你这个问题  但是
I feel like I'm always asking you this question, but...

498
00:31:44,850 --> 00:31:46,850
醒醒  坏脾气  醒醒
Wake up, Grump! Wake up!

499
00:31:46,850 --> 00:31:49,250
你有个具体的计划还是...
Is there an actual plan or...?

500
00:31:49,250 --> 00:31:52,350
只要一路飞到世界尽头
Just keep flying until we reach the end of the world.

501
00:31:52,350 --> 00:31:54,820
听起来很靠谱
Ah. Seems sensible.

502
00:31:55,610 --> 00:31:57,620
他们在哪里
So, where are they?

503
00:31:57,630 --> 00:31:59,560
显然已经离开了
Gone. Obviously.

504
00:31:59,560 --> 00:32:01,690
夜煞再一次从你手中
The Night Fury escaped you?

505
00:32:01,700 --> 00:32:03,860
-逃走了  -是我促成的
- Again? - I encouraged it.

506
00:32:03,870 --> 00:32:07,300
他们放弃了他们唯一的防守点
They've abandoned their only defensible position.

507
00:32:07,750 --> 00:32:11,300
带着一点可怜的家当  恐惧地逃离
Running scared with what little they can carry.

508
00:32:11,310 --> 00:32:13,210
没个尽头
It just keeps going.

509
00:32:13,210 --> 00:32:15,910
因为世界其实是圆的
That's 'cause the world is actually round.

510
00:32:15,910 --> 00:32:17,510
太阳是圆的  月亮是圆的
The sun's round. The moon is round.

511
00:32:17,510 --> 00:32:18,880
星星是圆的
Stars are round.

512
00:32:18,880 --> 00:32:20,710
尽管它们又小又蠢
Even though they're small and stupid.

513
00:32:22,340 --> 00:32:23,750
对吧  星星
Right? Stars.

514
00:32:23,750 --> 00:32:25,920
别气馁  他们跑不了多远
Don't fret. They won't get far.

515
00:32:25,920 --> 00:32:29,190
夜煞已经被干扰了
The Night Fury is distracted.

516
00:32:29,190 --> 00:32:32,890
我让他见到了你的母龙
I introduced him to your female.

517
00:32:32,900 --> 00:32:34,890
夜煞相配就相伴终身
Furies mate for life, you see.

518
00:32:34,900 --> 00:32:37,760
你发现了什么  伙计
What you picking up on, bud?

519
00:32:39,870 --> 00:32:41,370
光煞
The Light Fury!

520
00:32:41,370 --> 00:32:42,770
她在跟着我们
She's following us! Wow!

521
00:32:42,770 --> 00:32:44,770
好厉害
Cool.

522
00:32:46,810 --> 00:32:48,810
-你看  -她去哪里了
- Would ya look at that? - Where'd she go?

523
00:32:48,810 --> 00:32:50,780
她是天空做的吗
Is she made of sky?

524
00:32:50,780 --> 00:32:53,120
慢点  没牙仔
Whoa! Hold up, Toothless!

525
00:33:00,090 --> 00:33:01,920
看看这是谁
Well, look who it is.

526
00:33:04,630 --> 00:33:06,260
很高兴终于...
Oh, hey, it's really nice to finally...

527
00:33:17,740 --> 00:33:20,940
太棒了  真是太棒了
This is perfect. So great.

528
00:33:20,940 --> 00:33:22,780
都闭嘴
Not a word.

529
00:33:25,610 --> 00:33:28,170
对对对  但他们去哪里了
Y-Yes, yes, but where did they go?

530
00:33:28,890 --> 00:33:30,220
还得要我解释
I have to explain this.

531
00:33:30,220 --> 00:33:32,890
夜煞无法在寒冷的环境中生存
Night Furies can't survive in the cold,

532
00:33:32,890 --> 00:33:34,120
