They can only have gone...

540
00:33:59,850 --> 00:34:03,320
有人想猜一猜吗
Does anyone want to take a guess?

541
00:34:03,320 --> 00:34:04,750
有人吗
Anyone?

542
00:34:06,750 --> 00:34:08,890
东边
Ah, east!

543
00:34:08,890 --> 00:34:10,620
是西边
West.

544
00:34:10,630 --> 00:34:13,460
很简单吧
Hmm? Simple, you see?

545
00:34:13,460 --> 00:34:15,460
这不是很有趣吗
Oh, isn't this fun?

546
00:34:15,460 --> 00:34:17,630
