Yes? No?

547
00:34:19,300 --> 00:34:21,600
是的  是的
Yes. Yes.

548
00:34:21,600 --> 00:34:23,940
你对捕猎的爱呢
Where is your love of the hunt?

549
00:34:23,940 --> 00:34:26,470
